{"tid":1891173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗：武漢肺炎可能源自中国工人 恐散播各城市","createTime":"2020-02-21T15:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T01:12:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2bab7f2fee34092910f92c9b57e217b1a55e105d","tid":1891173,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"伊朗通訊社（IRNA）報導，伊朗衛生官員莫雷斯（Minou Mohrez）今天表示，冠狀病毒恐會散播至伊朗所有城市，官員也說，武漢肺炎可能來自境內中國工人。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，伊朗境內今天新增13起武漢肺炎確診病例，其中2人已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n衛生官員莫雷斯說：「根據目前的通報，冠狀病毒始於科姆市（Qom），我們注意到人流四處移動，病毒已擴散至伊朗好幾座城市，包括德黑蘭、巴博（Babol）、阿拉克（Arak）、伊斯法罕（Isfahan）、拉希特（Rasht）及其他城市，且有可能會散播至所有伊朗境內城市。」<br />\n<br />\n莫雷斯指出，伊朗爆發冠狀病毒源頭「可能為曾赴中國的科姆市中國工人」，但她並未進一步說明細節。<br />\n<br />\n有一家中國企業在科姆市蓋了一間太陽能發電廠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202002210394.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202002210394.aspx&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=63e4b612\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202002210394.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"6ab51565a9221ad2a2b4770a62088bab9628039b","tid":1891173,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"中國工人就是武漢肺炎既本體"},{"pid":"0ea44727a4bd22dc596409d09223a18274159bbb","tid":1891173,"uid":195380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒埋中東"},{"pid":"fd26306015f210eb852cef20f39314bd107b05fb","tid":1891173,"uid":326032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"Belt and Road <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f412bd3fb2b0eb733c00123777489797fe95aa","tid":1891173,"uid":1482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"一帶一路既成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190137ae5f072